CSS UNITS:-
there are multiple if units of css.
1.px-pixel-it is fixed for screen

2.%-percentage-it depends on their parent element

3.VW-viewport width,VH-viewport height
-it depends on total screen size ,if the screen size is small then they automatically adjust by the screen size.

4.VMAX-viewport maximum,VMIN-viewport minimum
-in vmax when the screen height is bigger than the screen with it will automatically stop and break their line into a new line
 EM&REM(Homework)
 5.EM-when we given a parent element value then that parent elementy is our 1em then automatically it reflects all the child element as well.

 6.REM-1 rem be alway 16 pixel.